								I'm a self-taught web developer from Hungary. I can use multiple programming languages and frameworks, built some developer tools I use myself, and delivered projects to clients. I work as a contactor, but I am always open to new opportunities.
								<br/>
								<br/>
								My focus is on writing the simplest, most elegant code that gets the job done, without unnecessary complexity.
							</p>
							<a
								href="/resume"
								target="_blank"
								rel="noreferrer noopener"
								class="text-white font-firamono text-md sm:font-lg flex gap-2"
							>
								<span class="border-b border-gray-500">my resume</span>
								@icons.External()
							</a>
							<ul
								class="text-md sm:text-lg flex flex-row flex-wrap gap-4 font-firamono text-gray-400"
							>
